The opposite of meta

This is actually interesting.

If meta moves upward…

then the opposite moves downward.

Not abstraction.

Instantiation.

Not

“What is the pattern?”

but

“What does Tuesday at 2:17 PM actually look like?”

Meta seeks invariants.

Its opposite seeks embodiment.

Both are required.

One without the other becomes either philosophy or bureaucracy.

